| Purpose | File Path |
|---------|-----------|
| Mail entity definitions | `/app/src/api/entities/tutanota/TypeRefs.ts` |
| Session key resolution | `/app/src/api/worker/crypto/CryptoFacade.ts` |
| Entity-REST interface | `/app/src/api/worker/rest/EntityRestClient.ts` |
| Decryption/mapping | `/app/src/api/worker/crypto/InstanceMapper.ts` |
| Mail wrapper (legacy/new) | `/app/src/api/common/MailWrapper.ts` |
| Mail loading logic | `/app/src/mail/model/MailUtils.ts` |
| Permission/bucket types | `/app/src/api/entities/sys/TypeRefs.ts` |
| Constants (PermissionType) | `/app/src/api/common/TutanotaConstants.ts` |

This architecture represents a migration from a simple permission-based model to a more scalable bucket-key based system while maintaining backward compatibility with legacy mails."}

